---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Kubernetes Platforms · EKS & GitOps Engineering"
  descripcion="Production-grade EKS and GKE clusters with Terraform, GitOps delivery via ArgoCD, and full observability. Kubernetes that engineers trust and operators can maintain."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2540 0%, #0d2f50 100%); padding: 100px 24px 80px;">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8" style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.15); color: #60A5FA; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.25);">
        Service · Kubernetes Platforms
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Kubernetes that runs in production,<br />not just in demos.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10" style="color: rgba(148,163,184,0.9);">
        Production-grade EKS and GKE clusters with Terraform, GitOps delivery via ArgoCD, full observability stack, and multi-tenant platform capabilities — from provisioning to Day 2 operations.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-px" style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,111,255,0.4);">
          Build my Kubernetes platform
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/solutions/kubernetes-adoption" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all hover:bg-white/10" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
          Kubernetes adoption path
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key points -->
  <section style="background: #F8FAFC; padding: 80px 24px;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">Everything a production Kubernetes platform needs</h2>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #64748B;">A running cluster is the start. Platform engineering is what makes it reliable, scalable, and maintainable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {[
          {
            title: 'Terraform-provisioned EKS & GKE',
            desc: 'Managed node groups with Karpenter autoscaling, IRSA/Workload Identity for pod-level AWS access, private API endpoints, and cluster add-ons (CoreDNS, VPC CNI, EBS CSI) all managed as code.',
            icon: 'M21 7.5l-9-5.25L3 7.5m18 0l-9 5.25m9-5.25v9l-9 5.25M3 7.5l9 5.25M3 7.5v9l9 5.25m0-9v9',
          },
          {
            title: 'GitOps with ArgoCD',
            desc: 'Application delivery driven by Git. Auto-sync with self-heal and pruning enabled. Drift detected and reconciled automatically. Rollbacks via git revert, not manual state manipulation.',
            icon: 'M17.25 6.75L22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3l-4.5 16.5',
          },
          {
            title: 'Full observability from day one',
            desc: 'kube-prometheus-stack for metrics, Loki for structured log aggregation, Jaeger for distributed tracing. Pre-built Grafana dashboards for cluster health, workload saturation, and SLO tracking.',
            icon: 'M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z',
          },
          {
            title: 'Shared Helm library & security policies',
            desc: 'Standard Helm library charts enforce resource requests/limits, liveness probes, PodDisruptionBudgets, and NetworkPolicies across every workload. OPA Gatekeeper for policy enforcement.',
            icon: 'M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z',
          },
        ].map(({ title, desc, icon }) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7" style="border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background: #EEF4FF;">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" style="color: #1E6FFF;" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d={icon} />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #0A2540;">{title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0A2540; padding: 80px 24px;">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready for a production-grade Kubernetes platform?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-10" style="color: rgba(148,163,184,0.85);">Schedule a platform assessment. We'll review your current cluster setup and design the platform layer that makes it reliable.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-px" style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(30,111,255,0.45);">
        Schedule platform assessment
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
